CBRE is pleased to offer for sale 19 Rowood Road, Prospect via an Expressions of Interest Campaign.

Key highlights include:
+ 15 year lease with 2 x 10 year options
+ Strong annual reviews
+ Building area of 4,800sqm*
+ Site area of 1.64Ha*
+ High clearance warehouse with sprinkler system throughout
+ Within the tightly held Prospect industrial precinct

For further information or to obtain an information memorandum, please contact the exclusive agents.

CBRE is excited to offer to market for sale 13 Rowood Road, Prospect via expressions of interest closing on Thursday 26th November 2020 at 4pm.

The building benefits from the below features:

+ Two buildings : 3,200 sqm*
+ Site Area: 9,074 sqm*
+ Short term lease back – suitable for owner occupiers
+ Prime location just off the M4 motorway on/off ramps
+ Flexible B5 zoning
+ Located nearby the popular ‘Prospect Homemaker Centre’

The property is being sold via expressions of interest closing on the Thursday the 26th November at 4pm.

For further information please contact the exclusive agents Elijah or Moshe from CBRE.


*approximate

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: EOI | FREESTANDING INDUSTRIAL BUILDING WITH LARGE YARD AREA | 3,200 SQM ON 9,074 SQM

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Arguably one of the best value industrial properties to enter the market in Western Sydney this year.

Older style yet desirable strata unit with excellent street frontage to Stoddart Road Prospect. The building is fully alarmed, has ducted air conditioned mezzanine offices and provides medium clearance warehousing with a minimum 5m internal clearance, accessed via 2 container height roller shutter doors. Zoning is 4(c) Special Industrial which allows for a range of uses including potential for Bulky Goods.

The property is within close proximity to the M4 Motorway, Great Western Highway and Prospect Highway.

For inspections please contact exclusive selling agents Greg Pike 0416 065 972 or Matthew Flynn 0409 323 690
